      <title>印度和南非在世贸组织谈判中阻止重大投资协议</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india-south-africa-block-investment-deal-wto-talks-2024-02-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度和南非在阿布扎比举行的世界贸易组织会议上正式反对一项投资协议，阻止该协议的通过，观察人士称此举可能会阻碍数千亿美元的投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/india-south-africa-block-investment-deal-wto-talks-2024-02-28/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 14:21:18 GMT</pubDate>
